N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4207.23 - Daily reports to commission

State Regulations

Each racing association conducting a race meeting shall
supply daily to the commission a report of the following: purse distribution; and such other data as may be required by the commission. The blank forms for
this purpose will be supplied by the commission. Notes
